47:02.319 --> 47:05.652
<i>He was the big, bad wolf.</i>

47:05.756 --> 47:09.248
<i>Now, the story is he got his name</i>
<i>from a dead man</i>

47:09.359 --> 47:12.522
<i>who came out the cemetery</i>
