<i>And he been howling</i>
<i>at the moon ever since.</i>

47:15.933 --> 47:19.300
<i>Oh, stop your train</i>

47:20.771 --> 47:24.207
<i>Let a poor boy ride</i>

47:24.308 --> 47:27.243
<i>Whoa, don't you hear me crying?</i>

47:34.785 --> 47:36.946
- You all right?
- Couldn't you get a smaller set?

