49:37.140 --> 49:38.937
I'm about to go wax this record, okay?

49:39.042 --> 49:41.738
Get your ass back over here, nigger.

49:48.518 --> 49:51.112
Now, you looking at my license, huh?

49:51.221 --> 49:55.021
