You got to sound that shit out.

50:07.671 --> 50:08.968
Come on.

50:09.306 --> 50:10.500
"Walter."

50:10.607 --> 50:12.632
Mud! The cops got Walter!

50:13.443 --> 50:16.003
- Hey, take it easy!
- Nigger.

50:16.113 --> 50:17.273
Come on. He works here.

50:17.381 --> 50:19.281
- He works here. Take it easy.
